---
import "@styles/global.module.css";
import Header from "@components/header.astro";
import Scripts from "@components/scripts.astro";
import Footer from "@components/footer.astro";
import Meta from "@components/meta.astro";
import Cursor from "@components/cursor.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <style>
      .btns button {
        background-color: #7289da;
        color: #fff;
        border: 0;
        padding: 0.5em 1em;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin: 0.5em;
      }

      .btns a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
    <Meta name="AkaBot" description="A Discord bot by Akatsuki" tag="discord bot, server management, anti raid, chat revive, chat streaks, chat summary, feedback commands, leveling, logging, moderation, polls, reaction roles, settings, welcoming, blocked users, premium features" />
    <Scripts />
    <Cursor />
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>AkaBot</h1>
      <p>A Discord bot by Akatsuki.</p>

      <div class="btns">
        <a
          href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1172922944033411243&permissions=2048&scope=bot"
        >
          <button>Invite</button>
        </a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/456zRGz75j">
          <button>Akabot support Discord server</button>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=DQSIkWdsW0yxEjajBLZtrQAAAAAAAAAAAANAAfkTJ5FUMVM1NjRJTVFZTEFMVlBWWUhGS1k1OENVTC4u"
        >
          <button>Suggest a feature/Report a bug</button>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p>
        The support Discord has active updates about the development of the bot,
        a chatting community and even you can be part of the development by
        suggesting new features!
      </p>
      <p>
        This Discord bot, crafted with care by a dedicated individual, provides
        numerous features to enrich your server experience. Below is a simple
        explanation of what this bot offers:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Anti Raid:</strong> This bot vigilantly monitors your server. If
          it detects a flurry of activities unfolding simultaneously, it sends you
          an alert, helping to ward off any potential raids on your server.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Chat Revive:</strong> When your chat goes dormant for a stretch,
          this bot can spur the conversation back to life.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Chat Streaks:</strong> If users send messages on successive days,
          this bot applauds these 'streaks', adding a fun element to your server
          interactions.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Chat Summary:</strong> Each day, this bot can provide a tally of
          messages sent on your server, helping you keep track of daily communication.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Feedback Commands:</strong> This bot can gather valuable remarks
          and suggestions from your users, fostering a feedback-rich environment.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Leveling:</strong> This bot can establish a 'levels' system, rewarding
          active users, and promoting engagement.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Logging:</strong> The bot can maintain a comprehensive record of
          activities on your server, ensuring transparency.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Moderation:</strong> The bot comes equipped with 'ban', 'kick',
          and 'timeout' commands, aiding you in maintaining harmony on your server.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Polls:</strong> With this bot, you can set up polls. Your users
          can then participate in these polls, promoting interaction.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Reaction Roles:</strong> This bot enables users to choose her
          roles by reacting to a message, adding a layer of interactivity.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Settings:</strong> You can tweak the bot's settings to align with
          your server's requirements.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Welcoming:</strong> The bot can relay personalized welcome and
          goodbye messages to users, adding warmth to your server.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Blocked Users:</strong> If required, you can restrict certain users
          from using the bot. This is a feature under your exclusive control.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Premium:</strong> The bot operator can bestow special privileges
          to certain users. This exciting feature will be introduced soon.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
